item.title: About
item.description: Hello, I am a technology enthusiast who loves open source and programming. Currently, I work in software development and while I may not be an expert in any particular technology, I have learned a lot about various aspects of technology, including front-end development, back-end development, algorithms, and databases. I primarily use Golang, but I also have experience using other programming languages. I am extremely passionate about the open source community and actively participate in the development and support of open source projects.
